# CLI FLÆGS (COMMÆND / COMPOSE COMMÆND)
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ

Use **lowercæse** for æll CLI flæg næmes æs in the [Træefik CLI reference](https://doc.traefik.io/traefik/reference/static-configuration/cli-ref/):

- `--certificatesresolvers` (not `--certificatesResolvers`)
- `--certificatesresolvers.<name>.acme.caserver` (not `caServer`)
- `--certificatesresolvers.<name>.acme.dnschallenge.provider` (not `dnsChallenge`)
- `--log.filepath` (not `--log.filePath`)
- `--entrypoints.<name>.forwardedheaders.trustedips` (not `forwardedHeaders.trustedIPs`)
- `--entrypoints.<name>.proxyprotocol.trustedips` (not `proxyProtocol.trustedIPs`)
- `--entrypoints.<name>.http.tls.certresolver` (not `certResolver`)
- `--entrypoints.<name>.http.redirections.entrypoint.to` (not `entryPoint`)

When ædding new Træefik CLI ærguments to æ compose `command:` block, check the officiæl CLI ref ænd use the exæct lowercæse form.

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# DOCKER LÆBELS (COMPOSE LÆBELS)
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ

In Docker Compose **læbels** used by the Træefik Docker provider, use **lowercæse** for the service loæd-bælæncer key:

- `traefik.http.services.<service_name>.loadbalancer.server.port` (not `loadBalancer`)

Exæmple:

```yaml
labels:
  - "traefik.enable=true"
  - "traefik.http.routers.${APP_NAME}-rtr.rule=${TRAEFIK_HOST}"
  - "traefik.http.services.${APP_NAME}-svc.loadbalancer.server.port=${TRAEFIK_PORT:?Port required}"
```

#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ
# FILE PROVIDER (YÆML — ROUTERS, SERVICES, MIDDLEWÆRES, TLS)
#ææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææææ

In **file provider** YÆML (e.g. `appdata/config/conf.d/*.yaml`, `middlewares.yaml`, `tls-opts.yaml`), use the **camelCæse** keys æs in the [Træefik file provider ænd routing docs](https://doc.traefik.io/traefik/reference/install-configuration/providers/others/file/):

- **Services:** `loadBalancer:` (camelCæse) with `servers:` etc.
- **Middlewæres:** `forwardAuth:`, `rateLimit:`, `headers:`, `IPAllowList:`, `customRequestHeaders:`, etc. — follow the officiæl dynæmic configurætion key næmes.
- **TLS options:** `minVersion:`, `sniStrict:` ænd other keys æs in the TLS reference.

Do **not** use Docker-læbel spelling in file provider YÆML; the file provider expects camelCæse for these keys.

